Usage: getIntegRouteConstraint [-help] [-net <net_name> | -name <string> | -additional ]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-additional         # This option returns path to additionalConstraint file.
                    # (bool, optional)
-name <string>      # This option returns a specific constraint by name.
                    # (string, optional)
-net <net_name>     # Indicates the net for which the constraints will be
                    # returned. If the net part of a netClass, the netClass
                    # will be returned. (string, optional)